OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781619074
OL,3,CRow over potential cull of endangered
OL,4,Chill ponies on Dartmoor
OL,6,FA row is growing over a potential cull
OL,7,Fof Dartmoor's hill ponies, as locals
OL,8,Fwarn officials' approach to conserving
OL,9,Fthe landscape will "devastate" numbers
OL,10,Fof the endangered breed.
OL,12,FCampaigners say requirements to cut
OL,13,Flivestock grazing on the moor's
OL,14,Fcommons under new contracts from the
OL,15,FGovernment's conservation agency
OL,16,FNatural England could lead to the
OL,17,Fremoval of up to 90% of its hill
OL,18,Fponies ` which would likely have to be
OL,19,Fculled.
OL,26,@qD@TOUqD@^O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781619074
OL,3,CRow over potential cull of endangered
OL,4,Chill ponies on Dartmoor
OL,6,FBut Natural England insists it wants
OL,7,Fto maintain numbers of the semi-wild
OL,8,Fponies on the moor "for generations to
OL,9,Fcome", while a Downing Street
OL,10,Fspokeswoman said it would not allow a
OL,11,Fcull of Dartmoor hill ponies and
OL,12,Finsisted the animals were safe under
OL,13,Fthe Labour Government.
OL,15,FDartmoor hill ponies have been on the
OL,16,Flandscape for 4,500 years, although
OL,17,Fnumbers have dwindled from 6,000 25
OL,18,Fyears ago to fewer than a thousand
OL,19,Ftoday, owing to historical policy
OL,20,Fchanges, and they have been declared
OL,21,Fan endangered breed, campaigners say.
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@EO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
