OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781619075
OL,3,CRow over potential cull of endangered
OL,4,Chill ponies on Dartmoor
OL,6,FThe Devon-based Friends of the
OL,7,FDartmoor Hill Pony charity is calling
OL,8,Ffor long-term, legal protection of the
OL,9,Fremaining hill pony herds in
OL,10,Frecognition of their rare status, and
OL,11,Fa separate agreed moor-wide herd size,
OL,12,Fas was in place with previous
OL,13,Fcontracts.
OL,15,FCampaigners also said Natural England
OL,16,Fshould wait for the outcomes of the
OL,17,FLand Use Management Group set up to
OL,18,Fimplement the recommendations of a
OL,19,Fgovernment-commissioned review in
OL,20,F2023, which is drawing up a land use
OL,21,Fplan for Dartmoor by 2027.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781619075
OL,3,CRow over potential cull of endangered
OL,4,Chill ponies on Dartmoor
OL,6,FAmid a growing row over the situation,
OL,7,FConservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Flabelled the situation as "total
OL,9,Fmadness" and demanded the Government
OL,10,Foverrule Natural England and make it
OL,11,Fstop immediately.
OL,13,F"Keir Starmer is on his way to making
OL,14,Fhis last acts in office the shameful
OL,15,Funderfunding of our military and the
OL,16,Fmass slaughter of Dartmoor ponies,"
OL,17,Fshe said.
OL,26,@pD@[OUqD@HO]uD@AOUxD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781619075
OL,3,CRow over potential cull of endangered
OL,4,Chill ponies on Dartmoor
OL,6,FA Downing Street spokeswoman said:
OL,7,F"So, let me be very clear on this:
OL,8,Fthis government will not allow a cull
OL,9,Fof Dartmoor ponies and we don't manage
OL,10,Fferal pony populations by culling in
OL,11,Fthis country.
OL,13,F"Natural England has not recommended a
OL,14,Fcull of Dartmoor ponies and it does
OL,15,Fnot have the power to order a cull and
OL,16,Fhas not advised one.
OL,18,F"And, more broadly, Dartmoor ponies
OL,19,Fare part of the cultural landscape of
OL,20,FDartmoor and play a vital role in the
OL,21,Fhealth of its moorland habitats."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUzD@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
