OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1781619075
OL,3,CRow over potential cull of endangered
OL,4,Chill ponies on Dartmoor
OL,6,FAn Environment Department (Defra)
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "In line with the
OL,8,FIndependent Review of Protected Site
OL,9,FManagement on Dartmoor, we are working
OL,10,Fwith partners, including the Dartmoor
OL,11,FHill Pony Association, to help ensure
OL,12,Fthat we maintain numbers of semi-wild
OL,13,Fponies on the moor for generations to
OL,14,Fcome."
OL,26,@oD@TOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
